1. *Izabrala* sam ovu haljinu za večeras. (I chose this dress for tonight.)
2. Ona je *izabrala* da ode na odmor umesto da ostane kod kuće. (She chose to go on vacation instead of staying at home.)
3. *Izabrala* sam najbolji restoran za našu proslavu. (I picked the best restaurant for our celebration.)
4. Kada sam *izabrala* fakultet, znala sam da je to pravi izbor za mene. (When I chose my college, I knew it was the right choice for me.)
5. Pre nego što *izabrala* šta ću obući, moram da vidim koji je dress code. (Before choosing what to wear, I need to see what the dress code is.)
6. Ona je *izabrala* da bude samostalna i otvori sopstveni biznis. (She decided to be independent and start her own business.)
7. Kada se *izabrala* nova predsednica udruženja, sve je postalo mnogo organizovanije. (When the new president of the association was elected, everything became much more organized.)
8. Imala sam teškoća da *izaberem* jednu omiljenu pesmu. (I had a hard time choosing one favorite song.)
9. Za ovo takmičenje, takmičari moraju *izabrati* tri kategorije u kojima će se takmičiti. (For this competition, participants must select three categories in which they will compete.)
10. Kada budemo *izabrali* novi automobil, želim da bude crvene boje. (When we choose a new car, I want it to be red.)